   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-a" mid="7" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> I really did not</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-b" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>A mercenary that desires for peace... how weird.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-c" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That's a great wish you have there.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-d" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Peace... that's why you said it's important to have peace.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>What I desire is... peace. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Chandler speaks with a serious expression which doesn't suit him at all.)</FONT><BR></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Why? Is it because I'm a fighter? I am not a gangster even though I fight. I fight to keep peace.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Tsk, that's I keep saying you're so young. Mercenaries aren't all about money, you know. You can't be a mercenary for a long time with that mindset.<FONT color=#7e12d2> (Chandler beats his chest with his fist.)</FONT> You need a burning passion inside here. Love, ambition, and desire! That's how you live a long life as a mercenary.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>You also must have a hope inside your heart... it will help you as you live your life. Even when surrounded by enemies, those with a hope deep in their hearts don't give up and give their all. That's how you live a long long life.<BR></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n032_warrior_master_chandler-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Chandler$<BR>Remembering things like that, you're quite the smart fellow! We must all put in our efforts to have peace. And we mercenaries are the ones who lend our power to protect and maintain that peace. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Chandler proudly stretches out his chest.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
